                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9364" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0609</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1440 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从“不明所以”到“得心应手”：福莱威尔的立体化培训之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From &quot;Unclear&quot; to &quot;Skilled&quot;: FREEWILL &#39;s Stereoscopic Training Path</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杨雪梅，张立明（通讯作者），张宗敏，肖瑾，冯静莹，杨承翰，张通，王汶节</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">昆明福莱威尔家具制造有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">轻工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福莱威尔；数字化转型；培训与开发；人才培养；</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FREEWILL; Digital transformation; Training and development; Talent cultivation;</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化转型成为当下企业发展的趋势，信息化建设、数字化技术为企业运营提供强劲支撑。数字化转型的过程中，实现人力资源管理制度化建设，落实员工培训措施对企业的可持续发展具有重要意义。福莱威尔作为集设计研发、销售服务、生产管理、软件研发为一体的专业家具企业，其人才培养理念和员工培训经验值得借鉴。本案例描述了福莱威尔决定自主研发可视化系统后，面对员工接受度低，可视化系统应用效果不佳等问题，采取的一系列完善人力资源培训制度，提高员工胜任能力，多元化人才培养措施。福莱威尔经历了“不明所以”到最终“得心应手”的转变，实现了人才与技术的双赢，打造出行业内专业化的“实效商学院”企业学堂。本案例可以用于引导学生思考企业如何分析各阶段的培训需求、采取科学高效的培训措施以及开发、储备人才的内在逻辑，并且掌握如何运用培训与开发的理论工具，分析实际问题以提出相应的对策，实现案例学习的目标。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Digital transformation has become a trend in the development of enterprises, and information construction and digital technology provide strong support for enterprise operations. In the process of digital transformation, the institutionalization of human resource management and the implementation of employee training measures are of great significance for the sustainable development of enterprises. As a professional furniture enterprise that integrates design and development, sales services, production management, and software development, FREEWILL&#39;s talent cultivation philosophy and employee training experience are worth learning from. This case describes the series of measures taken by FREEWILL to improve its human resources training system, enhance employee competence, and diversify talent cultivation, in response to issues such as low employee acceptance and poor application effectiveness of the visualization system, after deciding to independently develop a visualization system. FREEWILL has gone through a transformation from being &quot;Unclear&quot; to ultimately &quot;Skilled&quot;, achieving a win-win situation between talent and technology, and creating a specialized &quot;practical business school&quot; enterprise school in the industry. This case study can be used to guide students to think about how enterprises can analyze the training needs of each stage, adopt scientific and efficient training measures, and develop and reserve the internal logic of talent. They can also master how to use theoretical tools of training and development, analyze practical problems, and propose corresponding countermeasures to achieve the goal of case study learning.	</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《培训与开发》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">培训流程理论；培训需求分析；胜任力理论；利益相关者理论；培训评估模型</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-03</td>
                            </tr>
